OL,6,FTwo prolific thieves have been jailed
OL,7,Fafter a stealing more than #36,000
OL,8,Fworth of phones and accessories from a
OL,9,Fshop.
OL,11,FRobert Jody May, 51, and Joseph Perry,
OL,12,F42, raided the Three store in Montague
OL,13,FStreet in Worthing, Sussex in March.
OL,15,FMay drilled a hole through the wall of
OL,16,Fan adjoining property to gain access
OL,17,Fto the stock room while Perry is
OL,18,Fbelieved to have acted as a lookout.
