OL,6,FFootage showed Perry lingering in the
OL,7,Ftown centre, then later showed both
OL,8,Fmen carrying holdall bags as they
OL,9,Fentered a taxi.
OL,11,FFollowing a trial at Lewes Crown
OL,12,FCourt, both May and Perry were found
OL,13,Fguilty of burglary and have each been
OL,14,Fjailed for three years.
OL,16,FMay, of Whiterock Place, Southwick, is
OL,17,Fa prolific criminal with more than 50
OL,18,Fprevious convictions for more than 200
OL,19,Fprevious offences, many including
OL,20,Fburglary. Police say he has as many as
OL,21,F25 aliases.
