OL,6,FPerry, of Whitebeam Road, Northbrook,
OL,7,FWorthing, also has a prolific criminal
OL,8,Fhistory with 22 convictions for 57
OL,9,Fprevious offences, including 35 theft
OL,10,Frelated offences.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Andrew Ricks from
OL,13,FWorthing CID said: "Both men went to
OL,14,Fextensive lengths in order to steal
OL,15,Fmobile phones and accessories in
OL,16,FWorthing.
OL,18,F"Through a careful and thorough
OL,19,Finvestigation we were able to prove to
OL,20,Fthe jury how they carried out the
OL,21,Fburglary.
